title: MyFriendsHotGirl - Alexis Adams {19751 - 06.10.2015} NEW June 10
description: Alexis Adams thinks that her fiancee cheated on her while at the strip club. She's ready to call the wedding off when her fiancee's friend, Ike, stops by to calm her down. Alexis agrees to go through with the wedding on one condition, she gets to have fun before the wedding day with Ike. Ike agrees to go through with this all to make sure his buddy's wedding isn't ruined
